1. df mean disk free

$ df it show all but want to read

$ df -h --> human readable formate
$ df -H for gb
$ df --si --> si fr system intract
$ df -iH --> show inodes

$ df -H --total
$ df -h -t --> TYPES liker ext4

$ df -H -a --> all



2. du mean disk usage

use -h to human

du -h 
du --si --> in gb

du --si -s --> it show all summarise all and how big is it directory
du /tmp  /root --si -s 

du /tmp /root --si -s --total --> to see total of 2
